General.Name: Dominion Minerals Ltd
General.Description: Dominion Minerals Limited engages in the exploration of mineral properties. It holds a 100% interest in the Georgia Lime Project that comprises a mineral resource of high calcium limestone located in Georgia, the United States. The company was formerly known as Factor Therapeutics Limited and changed its name to Dominion Minerals Limited in September 2021. Dominion Minerals Limited was incorporated in 2002 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
